{"tid":1251422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣反擊﹗警隊唔係磨心，醫護先係﹗","createTime":"2019-06-22T13:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T17:37:49.000Z","uid":229880,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd5419147adf476005cda31c437f0478ccf2376","tid":1251422,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:50:56.000Z","msg":"21/6過後，我地要更進一步加強文宣戰﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日李思嫣班人開始出返黎，明顯已經又有人出錢搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n或者想好似689時期咁，<strong>發起群眾鬥群眾嘅模式</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n因此，我地唔好俾輿論慢慢轉，<br />\n呢一刻絕對要以正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />﹗盡快鞏固各個界別支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />﹗<br />\n<br />\n例如︰<br />\n好多人傳黎傳去，成日講警隊好辛苦，企係中間好慘&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<strong>偏偏中立嘅香港人好容易受流言左右，慢慢更可能令輿論對我地做成壓力。</strong><br />\n因此，我地必須終止廢話傳黎傳去﹗<br />\n<br />\n我地要強調，<strong>示威者每日自發出黎都一樣辛苦﹗仲要出黎嘅人係保護緊香港社會</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />﹗<br />\n講個例子，有d人成日笑大學生走830早堂，但係有無留意係呢兩個星期&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n出去嘅學生只有早到，絕無遲到﹗<br />\n12/6 未到800已經係唒龍和道﹗21/6 仲要約730﹗<br />\n佢地為既係乜野？<strong>咪就係為左大家住緊嘅香港囉&hellip;&hellip;</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果唔想再鬥辛苦就應該一齊請警隊放低武器﹗<br />\n再者，政府用緊警隊企前面黎保護自己，警隊又點唔會係磨心﹗<br />\n即係︰<strong>市民 vs. (警隊)政府</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一步，我地要破局就要做到孤立政府同警隊嘅局面﹗<br />\n除左繼續要求<strong>成立獨立調查委員會</strong>，等淺藍班人動搖之外，<br />\n亦令為警隊護航嘅人醜態百出，近嘅增強我地士氣，遠嘅亦有利於幾個月後嘅區選。<br />\n<br />\n同時，我地要同社會講清楚醫護人員先反而變成磨心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n明明醫護出勤一心而救人，點知人未必即時救到，仲要過程俾狗欺壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />﹗<br />\n附上啱啱嘅隔離post，<br />\nHA secret 爆料： 昨晚警員無登記就自行離開醫院！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cRMdQT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cRMdQT</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>係度順度對呢兩個星期默默守護緊香港嘅醫護人員，講聲多謝</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />﹗<br />\n<br />\n而既然醫護人員咁好，成日保護我地，又俾狗恰，<br />\n咁我地就更應該強化醫護成為我地強而有力嘅支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n相信仲要有一段時間要大家一齊努力&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n請香港人加油﹗﹗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddefbca89a3b7940c3bc1c527d836edcd41b70a","tid":1251422,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960d6c006e0469b2ced190263686aa0aaeb48d41","tid":1251422,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88c6fce655b0edd849e880286bb9abc7a22455a","tid":1251422,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faa67a982e4f6e77034b691b7d008ba9a3ee1d0","tid":1251422,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747f9e90685eab555af6586d71cdc57b5338c37c","tid":1251422,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"推下！"},{"pid":"85124fe1f2d95f0cbd31963381917e29304b1d5e","tid":1251422,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"